F

Flight - Class in com.csci4448.project.model
This class creates getter and setter for the variables in Flight and has a helper function Flight that holds information for a flight that is used in the FlightController class.
Flight(String, String, int, int, int, String, double, int) - Constructor for class com.csci4448.project.model.Flight
This is a helper function that create appropriate variables for flights and give each an id so the user can choose from the available flights in the FlightController class.
FlightController - Class in com.csci4448.project.controller
This class creates flights, stores them in myFlight list and uses two methods in PathFinder and PathFinderView to access all of the locations and uses myFlight list of flight information to display to the user.
FlightController() - Constructor for class com.csci4448.project.controller.FlightController
 
flightInfo() - Static method in class com.csci4448.project.controller.FlightController
Creates flights and stores flight information in myFlight.
flightNum - Variable in class com.csci4448.project.model.Flight
 
flightRun() - Static method in class com.csci4448.project.controller.FlightController
This method is used to call searchFlight in PathFinder class to select locations.
FlightView - Class in com.csci4448.project.view
This class iterates through the list of available locations in the PathFinder class in which the customer would then choose a starting location and end location.
